        "subject": "LU-2825 lustre: Shrink sizes of cl_page and cl_req structures",
        "message": "LU-2825 lustre: Shrink sizes of cl_page and cl_req structures\n\nFor cl_page, changed the position of cp_ref, cp_state, cp_flags and\ncp_type to better suit the alignment. Converted cp_flags and cp_type\nmembers to bitfields. This leads to a saving of 16 bytes for cl_page\nstructure.\n\nFor cl_req, changed the position of crq_nrpages. This leads to a\nsaving of 8 bytes for cl_req structure.\n\nSigned-off-by: Swapnil Pimpale <spimpale@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Id74e22cbed656f80f0fd8e63bf83c9dd680742e4\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
